---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="TripSquad — Terms of Service" description="TripSquad's terms of service.">

<main class="legal">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <p>By using TripSquad you agree to these terms. If you don't agree, please don't use the app.</p>

    <h2>Accounts</h2>
    <p>You must be at least 13 years old. You're responsible for keeping your password secure and for anything that happens under your account.</p>

    <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
    <p>Don't use TripSquad to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Harass, bully, or impersonate other users.</li>
      <li>Spam, scrape, or disrupt the service.</li>
      <li>Break the law in any way.</li>
      <li>Upload or share illegal, abusive, or copyright-infringing content.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We can suspend or terminate accounts that violate this, at our discretion, with or without notice.</p>

    <h2>Your content</h2>
    <p>You keep ownership of trip plans, chats, and other content you create. By using the service, you grant us a limited license to store and display your content so we can deliver the service to you and your squad.</p>

    <h2>AI output (Scout)</h2>
    <p>Scout gives travel suggestions generated by an AI model. We don't guarantee accuracy — prices, availability, and safety conditions change. Always verify with the airline, hotel, or official source before booking or travelling.</p>

    <h2>Paid features</h2>
    <p>The core app is free. Any paid features will be clearly marked. Subscriptions auto-renew unless cancelled; cancel through your app store account settings.</p>

    <h2>Third parties</h2>
    <p>TripSquad may link to or integrate with third-party services (Supabase, Anthropic, Firebase, Apple, Google). We're not responsible for their content or policies.</p>

    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>TripSquad is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We don't guarantee the service will be uninterrupted or error-free. To the fullest extent permitted by law, Afia Labs is not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the app.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update these terms. If we make a material change, we'll notify you in the app or by email. Continued use after changes means you accept the new terms.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hi@afialabs.net">hi@afialabs.net</a>.</p>
  </div>
</main>

<style>
  .legal { padding: 80px 24px 120px; min-height: 100vh; }
  .container { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  h1 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 40px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--ts-text); }
  .updated { color: var(--ts-muted); margin-bottom: 32px; font-size: 14px; }
  h2 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--ts-lime); }
  p, li { color: var(--ts-text2); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; }
  ul { padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  a { color: var(--ts-lime); }
</style>

</BaseLayout>
